==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Surfle
<hw>Sur"fle</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v.
t.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Sulphur</er>.]</ety> <def>To wash, as the face,
with a cosmetic water, said by some to be prepared from the
sulphur.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She shall no oftener powder her hair, [or] <qex>surfel</qex> her
cheeks, . . . but she shall as often gaze on my picture.</q>
<rj><qau>Ford.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surfer</ent>⟦br⟧
